.row.inbox-header
  .col-lg-3 Started By
  .col-lg-4 To: Subject
  .col-lg-4 Last Reply By
  .col-lg-1 Delete




- @received_cases.each do |rcase|
  .row.inbox-content
    .col-lg-3
      .base= rcase.originator.full_name
      .meta= rcase.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %l:%M %p")

    .col-lg-4
      .base
        = rcase.patient.first_name
        = ":"
        %span.subject= rcase.subject
      .meta Unread
    .col-lg-4 
    .col-lg-1.deleter 
      %i.fa.fa-times

